# 🏥 Medical Warehouse Inventory Management System (MWIMS) – Setup Guide

This guide explains how to set up and run the MWIMS project locally with Node.js and MySQL.

---

## 💻 Requirements

### Software:
- Node.js (v16 or later)
- MySQL Server (v8.x)
- Browser (Chrome/Edge)
- Code Editor (VS Code recommended)

### Node.js Packages:
- `express`
- `mysql2`
- `socket.io`
- `cors`

